      <title>美国 4 月份服务业萎缩；价格压力再度加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-service-sector-contracts-april-price-pressures-reaccelerate-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国服务业3月份出现萎缩，而企业为投入支付的价格指标则大幅上涨，这是通胀前景令人担忧的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-service-sector-contracts-april-price-pressures-reaccelerate-2024-05-03/</guid>
