    <item>
      <title>美联储鲍曼支持当前政策立场，但仍看到通胀风险</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-bowman-supports-current-policy-stance-still-sees-inflation-risks-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事米歇尔·鲍曼周五表示，即使美联储将基准利率稳定在当前水平，通胀也应继续下降，同时重申，如果进展减弱或出现逆转，她愿意提高政策利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-bowman-supports-current-policy-stance-still-sees-inflation-risks-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 13:52:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
