      <title>由于劳动力市场降温，美国就业增幅为六个月以来最低</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-job-growth-slows-april-unemployment-rate-rises-39-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国4月就业增长放缓幅度超预期，年薪涨幅近三年来首次跌破4.0%，但由于劳动力市场仍然相当紧张，现在预期美联储在9月前开始降息可能为时过早。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-job-growth-slows-april-unemployment-rate-rises-39-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:35:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
